Real, Barcelona Face UEFA Disciplinary Cases After Champions League Match

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-04-28T15:45:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/real-barcelona-face-uefa-disciplinary-cases-after-champions-league-match.html
European soccer’s ruling body UEFA
said it opened disciplinary cases against Real  Madrid  and
Barcelona after incidents at last night’s Champions League
semifinal first-leg match, which Barcelona won 2-0 in Madrid.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
